    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the Administrator of <strong><i>Separium</i></strong>. Complete AI Purry's mission—to assess anomalies in the elevator—and reach the Administrator's Office on the 12th floor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow these steps to proceed:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rotate counterclockwise and memorize the elements that belong to the Separium elevator.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Determine if this elevator is normal or anomalous. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If it is normal, choose to &quot;Retain&quot; the elevator. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If it is anomalous, exit through the door to escape from the elevator.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If your judgment is correct, the elevator will ascend one floor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upon reaching the 12th floor, review Purry's final question.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Based on your answer, Purry will decide whether you qualify as the Administrator.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >/ <br><strong><i>Separium: 12th Elevator</i></strong> is a game simulation set in the fictional space of <strong><i>Separium</i></strong> within Team Pearl’s sci-fi universe, <strong><i>Sepafuturism</i></strong>. It draws inspiration from the liminal space genre and <i>The Exit 8</i>.</p>",
